This isn't my #mood it's my #mentality. MONEY IS NOT REAL. The time and energy *SPENT* to obtain this paper (and now it's just digital numbers on screens) is the REAL CURRENCY. Your power, your #energy, your time, your skill, your creativity, etc. is the TRUE VALUE of any "work." YOU are the power that be.... Let that sink in...
I'm forever grateful that someone questioned why I was doing what I was doing for someone else, rather than for myself. I'm forever grateful for my #intuition that told me to never do anything for money, do it for a deeper meaning, do it for a TRUE purpose, do it for the love of it. I'm forever grateful that I am not the first, or last, to feel this way. I am not a "pioneer" of this ideology, but I will be an embodiment of it, as much as possible.
I have no shame whatsoever saying I have $0.00. We need to transform our dis-eased mentality from believing no money means being "broke" to seeing it as being "free"..... These words are being used to control our minds and the way we think/feel about "money." It's all a game of monopoly, we all know it controls us at some level of #consciousness.
Once you become fully aware, or as I say "once I stopped lying to myself," you will see the game being played... WE'RE being played. You can keep "hustlin and grindin" all you want but it's NOT what you want, I know this as my #internal #truth and I know it's #universal. I know we really just want what we NEED, and that would suffice. Don't fall for the materialism/consumerism/slavery scam. This is why I say we need to #wakeup.
This life is so much more valuable, it's #sacred, there's so much more it has to offer us, FOR FREE... #spiritual #economics #mental #freedom the link in my bio is my gift to you if you are open to receiving🙏🌱
